OL,4,G2100FLiza Minnelli: The Last Heiress
OL,5,     Fof Hollywood
OL,6,     GThis documentary is a portrait of
OL,7,     Gan exceptional American talent,
OL,8,     Gunforgettable in her role as
OL,9,     GSally Bowles in Cabaret.
OL,10,G2215FGlenn Close: A Feminist Force
OL,11,     GGlenn Close embodies neither
OL,12,     GHollywood's beauty standards nor
OL,13,     Gits sugar-coated perfection. The
OL,14,     Gactress portrays women fighting
OL,15,     Gfor equality and their strength
OL,16,     Gto rise again.
